    dc:description "FIGURE 74. Lasianthus lucidus Blume (A–D & G–H from Dang 405 and E–F & I–J from Dang 416, VNM and the herbarium of Iriomote Station (Japan)): A. Branch with fruits, B. Close-up of expanding young leaves, C. Stipules, D. Abaxial leaf surfaces, E–F. Inflorescence showing side view flower buds, G. Flower bud and fruits, H–J. Young and mature fruits." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7571780/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

